reviewText:
It is a great movie. I was looking for this movie for the longest time and I was so happy when I saw that amazon had it so I ordered it.
Unfortunately, I had to return it, the quality was so bad you can even see the imagine clear enough, and the sound was so bad. So i am waiting to see if they offer a better quality of movie so I can re-order it. I'm checking off an on to see, if I can find this movie.
